#: content/showcase/case-studies/qgis_at_financial_times/qgis_at_financial_times.md:63
msgid ""
"**QGIS**: Can you tell us a bit about yourself? What\\'s your educational "
"background? What did you do before joining the data visualization team at "
"FT?"
msgstr ""

#: content/showcase/case-studies/qgis_at_financial_times/qgis_at_financial_times.md:67
msgid "![](./images/ft_gotthard-tunnel.png){.align-left width=\"60.0%\"}"
